Functioning of Computer 
-----------------------
  
The Functioning of Computer undergoes three stages.
1.Input Stage (Things to Work upon)
2.Process Stage (The actual work being performed)
3.Output Stage (The Result)

Functional Component of Computer
--------------------------------- 

Input Unit

The input unit formed by the input device attached to the computer.
example:  Mouse,keyboard

* An input unit takes the input and converts into binary form so that it can be understood by Computer. 




